<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-191] Update pacemaker link in Lustre Operations Manual</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-191</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Michael Schwartzkopff &amp;lt;misch@clusterbau.com&amp;gt; is currently updating a version of an article he wrote about &quot;Using Pacemaker with Lustre&quot; for the lustre.org wiki.  The version he is working on is currently posted at &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Documentation&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Documentation&lt;/a&gt;. The earlier version is also posted there to which a link has been made from the Lustre Operations manual (Chapter 11 &quot;Configuring Lustre Failover&quot;).  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When Michael completes his work, the link in the manual should be updated so it points to the updated version of Michael&apos;s paper.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
